    <abstract id="aspace_97f38f34229ebf4bddc63a4e60f332f8" label="Abstract">The Knights of Equity, Court 9, Pittsburgh, Pa. Records consist of the constitution, minute books, programs, a scrapbook, and photographs for the period 1936-1977.</abstract>
